################################################################################
# RESTFX-DDD PROJECT — .dockerignore
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# PURPOSE:
#   Defines which files are excluded from Docker build context to:
#   • Reduce image size.
#   • Speed up build times.
#   • Prevent accidental leaks of secrets or local configs.
#
# GUIDELINES:
#   1. Exclude all developer or temporary files (logs, coverage, vendor, .env).
#   2. Include only code and build manifests needed for compiling.
#   3. Allowlist (`!`) key directories such as cmd/, internal/, pkg/, config/.
#
# EFFECT:
#   A minimal, clean Docker context that ensures reproducible builds across
#   local and CI environments.
#
# MAINTENANCE:
#   • Keep in sync with .gitignore where applicable.
#   • Verify each service’s Dockerfile builds successfully after pruning.
#   • Run `docker build --no-cache .` after modifications to validate context.
################################################################################

